\ matrix1d-range: build a 1xN matrix from start/end/step.

\ Basic ascending sequence
1.0 5.0 1.0 matrix1d-range .

\ Ascending with non-unit step
0.0 10.0 2.5 matrix1d-range .

\ Descending sequence
10.0 0.0 -2.0 matrix1d-range .

\ Single-element matrix (start = end)
3.0 3.0 1.0 matrix1d-range .

\ End not on an exact step boundary — last element is < end
0.0 10.0 3.0 matrix1d-range .

\ Step zero rejected
1.0 5.0 0.0 matrix1d-range

\ Step sign / direction mismatch rejected
1.0 5.0 -1.0 matrix1d-range
